## Connectivity to the Internet

Curl is a tool just like ping to test connectivity of a network, while ping checks if one can contact another, curl is used to transfer data to and from a server.

I used curl to test the connectivity between my public server and nexwork.org, https://learn.nextwork.org/projects/aws-host-a-website-on-s3, example.com

### Ping vs Curl

Ping and curl are different because ping checks if one can contact another, while curl is used to transfer data to and from a server

